technologyreview.com/2026/06/01/1138207/the-download-china-bci-brain-implant-nvidia-ai-chips-laptops/", "source": "MIT Tech Review", "image": null, "score": 3}, {"id": "https://the-decoder.com/?p=36160", "title": "Turing Award winner Richard Sutton says pure generative AI can't do real science", "summary": "Turing Award winner Richard Sutton sees a central weakness in conventional generative AI: it can't evaluate its own results. Without that ability, real scientific discovery remains impossible: novelty flickers briefly and is lost again. Systems like AlphaGo or AlphaProof show that only built-in eval...", "link": "https://the-decoder.com/turing-award-winner-richard-sutton-says-pure-generative-ai-cant-do-real-science/", "source": "The Decoder", "image": null, "score": 2}, {"id": "https://the-decoder.com/?p=36136", "title": "Nvidia's Nemotron 3 Ultra becomes the smartest open US model, but China still leads", "summary": "According to benchmark platform Artificial Analysis, Nvidia's new Nemotron 3 Ultra is the most capable open AI model from the US to date.", "link": "https://the-decoder.com/nvidias-nemotron-3-ultra-becomes-the-smartest-open-us-model-but-china-still-leads/", "source": "The Decoder", "image": null, "score": 2}], "today_tech": [{"id": "oai:arXiv.org:2606.01639v1", "title": "RRP-Voice: A Longitudinal Dataset and Benchmark for Recurrent Respiratory Papillomatosis Detection", "summary": "Abstract: Deep learning has advanced pathological voice detection rapidly, yet rare laryngeal diseases remain underexplored due to data scarcity. Recurrent Respiratory Papillomatosis (RRP) exemplifies this gap: an HPV-induced disease of the larynx in which patients oscillate between recurrence and p...", "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.01639", "source": "arXiv Audio & Speech", "image": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.01639v1/2606.01639v1/Figures/all_longitudinal.png", "score": 15}, {"id": "oai:arXiv.org:2606.00079v1", "title": "BitsMoE: Efficient Spectral Energy-Guided B