ors for subtle grammatical distinctions, and Supervised Fine-Tuning (SFT) with Maximum Likelihood Estimation fails to opt...", "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.00020", "source": "arXiv NLP", "image": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.00020v1/2606.00020v1/x1.png", "score": 9}]}